---
title: Chimichurri Steak with Roasted Potato Wedges and Green Salad
description: Chimichurri is an Argentinean herb sauce that pairs exceptionally well with steak. We're kicking off the Victoria Day long weekend with this classic steak and potatoes pairing. Here's a tip: if you have a barbecue, we heartily suggest grilling the steak and potatoes on it!
